Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:02:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  有什么事吗  凛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛  早上好
Comment: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,↓Title↓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\pos(424,450)\fs+4\b0\3c&H41acff}我的住所
Comment: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,↑Title↑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.91,0:02:17.86,comment1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上午是晴天  但下午会下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:21.90,comment1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建议大家早点把晾的衣服收回
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛  今早你做了什么梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦？ 我做梦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  还在梦里叫了我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是枫差点被外星人捉去做活体实验
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是脑袋很大的长这样眼睛的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…是刚想出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦别去管了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做家务  完成作业  准备这么费事的早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还做了便当
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说做梦  连睡觉时间也没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都睡得很好哦  早上醒来时也很有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正叔叔已经出差了  简单地做些饭就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也要放松一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么行…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于我来说  能照顾凛是唯一的生存意义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我去放松…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就随你喜欢的去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天的便当是西京烧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.27,0:03:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭也会努力做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上也发生了一件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是能出现在凛的梦里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在震动…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银行的存折…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个等一下再拿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快躲到桌子下面避难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着桌子逃跑就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样  用湿手绢捂住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…手绢都收拾到衣柜里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停  停了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉  真冷静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾是一定  一定  小枫-KKK所属
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中林  一号  科学部部长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢  喜欢  小希-SSS所属
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中林  二号  科学部副部长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灿烂  灿烂  小琳-RRR所属
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中林  三号  科学部经理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合三人之力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲卫队合体  中林三兄弟！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧  土见凛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用运动部收集的精选特臭袜子味道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你臭得无法让女生接近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受天罚吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给凛大人添麻烦的人决不原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再有下次可就要用长椅了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴兄弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  凛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们的关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知该怎么道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:06:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要介意  以前也是这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是托你们两个的福  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是预备铃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  枫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这部分要在下次的考试里出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道会出还搞错的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是无可救药的笨蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无可救药的笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我也一样  放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是值得骄傲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛大人  我记了笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下请让我来教你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小琳  也帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小琳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带来了吧  快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  凛大人  这是便当
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都想让凛大人尝尝…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莉奈的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经这么会做饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:07:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…做了这么多？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点兴奋过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这是我的自信之作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.16,0:08:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎鸡蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  只有煎鸡蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有酱油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起种类更注重数量吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黏糊糊的搅鸡蛋煎成软绵绵的煎鸡蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛我的心意也有了形状
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎么的感觉好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这么多有点吃不下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天刚好特别想吃煎鸡蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  凛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  我要吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃  奈莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  凛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太天真了  凛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包含着女孩子爱的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人的话  即使胃会胀裂也要全部吃下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然囫囵吞枣地吃了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷的心和胃绝不会拒绝女性的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛还是缺乏对女生的温柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你  凛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胃药
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了  枫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛是过分温柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就去拿水来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛你不需要喝水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该尝尝人生的酸甜苦辣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有一点变小的迹象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  死心吧  回不了家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  你应该对万事死心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们决不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲卫合体队  中林三兄弟  合体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干呢  在干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛没什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一起回去没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想学几个新菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  小凛也真让人羡慕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  我能做的只有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  伞…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.01,0:11:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西叽里咕噜的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:11:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  无法继续问下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还没见到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫…枫…枫！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒加上过度疲劳造成体力下降
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:12:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让病人安静地休息一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早饭就由我来接着做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫醒了的话必须让她吃点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉  来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不能做成那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛  水平好烂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会惹枫生气的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  男人不应该轻易放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水  水  水  水…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候加水可是不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的我来做就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛  你不去学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天决定休息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我竟然让凛不能去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我添麻烦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫就在房里安心休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就交给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello  小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食堂的炸面包和习题给你带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚沙前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得你们二位可能会愁没有东西吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不嫌弃的话可不可以让我们来做？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是我的工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  枫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须给枫做些补充体力的东西吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有我就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去帮忙清扫房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小琳  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小希  救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  不要吸得那么用力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么可以帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近和凛在一起的时间变少了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前都是由我来照顾他的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被他讨厌了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是被称为“惊愕的时雨”的亚沙前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“惊愕的时雨”是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为亚沙前辈明明看起来不像会做饭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.19,0:17:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但做饭非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到这个名字我才比较吃惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葵纳豆怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把秋葵这么伟大的食物和纳豆搅在一起…太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来到人界以来第一次遇到这么过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻飘飘的甜甜的煎鸡蛋里面  加了章鱼的发酵物是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是明石烧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说是章鱼烧的始祖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌章鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊愕的时雨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳豆…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  普莉姆拉  枫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说没有食欲在睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛  好像很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  今天实在是太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没做什么了不起的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  其实什么都没做…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这回事  帮我大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再有什么事的时候就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天在学校见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:19:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体变虚弱了可以吃药
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能治好虚弱心灵的人可就只有小凛你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（用微波炉热一下就可以了,不要弄糊了!!）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫  一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只吃一点也好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是对不起了  凛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊  生病了就要好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我有用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是凛的累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实就算我不在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来地震吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.84,0:20:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  枫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都这么努力照顾我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…累赘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有枫  我什么都不会做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也可以让我照顾你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要向我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候要稍稍放松一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是枫倒下了  又会像今天一样引起骚动了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.34,0:21:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早饭已经做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  喝了莉姆给我的药一下子就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉的药？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  原来那时是在给枫磨药啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你  这是换的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁早饭还没凉快点起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是和平常一样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说要稍稍放松点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  已经放松了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常一直是5点半起床
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:22:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天多睡了5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是睡太多了脑袋会疼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天开始还是5点半起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先下去了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,↓Trailer↓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.34,0:23:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选哪个椅子才好呢  真头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.93,0:24:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个的攻击力有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.98,0:24:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击力？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.06,0:24:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不试试的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.29,0:24:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要抡起来?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.52,0:24:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  SHUFFLE  第6话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.99,0:24:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.18,0:24:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛  就决定选这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.29,0:24:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么选择方法啊…
